channel.title: Proper Minigame Interfaces
channel.description:
Thanks to those guys who gave out the ticket and catapault interfaces, they helped me a lot.
Interface ID for Proper Castle Wars is 11146 Interface ID for Tears of Guthix is 3279 (Must be placed as a sidebar) Interface ID for Kingdom Management Screen on Etceteria is 10984 Interface ID for Agility Arena is 8287. Interface ID for Wilderness is 197. Interface ID for Proper Gnomeball is 4958. Interface ID for Temple Repair in Shades of Mort'ton is 4959. Interface ID for Fight Pits viewing screen is 3209.(Must be used as sidebar.) Interface ID for Fight Pits winner notice is 2804. Interface ID for confirmation screen of Duel Arena is 6412.
You can test these first by typing ::interface IDNUMBER.
Now most of these don't work as they do in RuneScape if you use them as interfaces. Most of the experienced coders know how to do this, and if you really need to know how to do it, I'll tell you if you give me the Interface IDs for the Trawler and Tutorial Island.
